5728   // extended mul fulfills the other requirements.
5729   // For example, reduce.add(ext(mul(ext(A), ext(B)))) is still a valid partial
5730   // reduction since the inner extends will be widened. We already have oneUse
5731   // checks on the inner extends so widening them is safe.
5732   std::optional<TTI::PartialReductionExtendKind> OuterExtKind;
